data.description: Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a captivating residence in the prestigious Forrester Heights community, nestled at 304 Roanoake Way, Greenville, SC. This remarkable property is strategically positioned in an enviable locale, boasting top-rated schools and convenient proximity to a plethora of amenities.  This splendid house offers a spacious layout featuring four bedrooms, three and a half bathrooms, a well-appointed office, and a delightful sunroom. Meticulous attention has been given to its recent makeover, with fresh paint adorning not only the walls but also the ceilings, and thorough cleaning, inside and out, to transform it into a truly beautiful abode.  Residents of this community are further treated to an array of amenities, including a refreshing pool, tennis court, and inviting common areas. Additionally, the property itself boasts a generously sized, fully fenced backyard, perfect for hosting gatherings with friends and family or savoring quality moments together.  The kitchen is thoughtfully designed and fully equipped with state-of-the-art appliances, offering abundant countertop space for culinary endeavors and meal preparation. Each of the bedrooms exudes a sense of spaciousness, providing ample room for furniture arrangements and storage solutions. The master bedroom enjoys the luxury of an en-suite bathroom, complete with a generously sized bathtub and a separate shower, adding an extra layer of comfort and convenience.  This outstanding opportunity is now even more irresistible, with a recent price reduction specifically for the flooring. Don't let this chance slip through your fingers to own a stunning home in this prime location. Reach out to our dedicated real estate agent today to schedule a viewing and make your dreams of homeownership a reality.
